description: Our family has launched Nana G's Chicken and Waffles. We are Serving an American Tradition on a Rolling Kitchen. Nana G is 104 years old and loves her chicken. She has been making Chik-n-Waffles for family and friends for nearly 75 years.  So, we have decided to take her recipes to the streets.Nana G's Chik-n-Waffles is family-owned and operated in . Other companies may offer similar services, but our services are the best, and you'll leave feeling apart of our extended family.If you’re looking for street food with high quality and personal service, you’ve come to the right "Food Truck." At Nana G's Chik-n-Waffles we’ll give you the attention and personal service you’ll come to expect and enjoy just as if you were sitting at her table. We offer the best in "Fried Chicken and Homemade Waffles."  Nana G's Chik-n-Waffles may be "New" to the street scene but her recipe's goes back 75 years.  Allow us to share this experience with you.
name: Nana G's Chik-n-Waffles
